test: LAN Any UDP Untrusted (35)
expect block in on eth1 proto udp from 8.8.8.8 to 8.8.4.4 port 1234

test: LAN Any ICMP Untrusted (36)
expect block in on eth1 proto icmp from 8.8.8.8 to 8.8.4.4 port 0

test: LAN to LAN Trusted (37)
expect pass in on eth1 proto tcp from 10.0.0.5 to 10.0.0.6 port 80

test: LAN to LAN Untrusted (38)
expect block in on eth1 proto tcp from 8.8.8.8 to 10.0.0.6 port 80

